{"id":441617,"date":[{"year":1963,"month":3,"day":26}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"372","ytitle":"","mtitle":"纸老虎出笼","ftitle":"——肯尼迪圣约瑟之行","authors":["萧丁"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧丁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春来烦恼已重重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又听响丧钟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放眼南天红半壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烽烟滚滚“后院”中，　 人在火边烘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愁满面，恨填胸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疯狂扑向火熊熊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要筑围墙高千尺，①"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暂时隔火又遮风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鬼计实无穷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瘟神最怕露行踪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难得出深官。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老艾余悸今犹在，②"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尼克衣衫带蛋痕。③"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧事够丧魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开摩托，泊艨艟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞机天上闹嗡嗡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"护驾莫放松。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽车铁甲严封，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"置身“保险箱”中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕西红柿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何愁石块轰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑骂由人我自且从容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看他来势汹汹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俨然盖世英雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可惜心惊加肉跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但愁处处遇刀丛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还摆啥威风!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破绽难缝，破绽难缝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是深山母大虫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但见纸皮包竹骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颤颤抖抖命将终。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注:①肯尼迪在圣约瑟叫嚷:“我们将在古巴周围构筑一道围墙。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"②艾森豪威尔一九六○年远东之行，一路挨揍，回到檀香山，还惊魂未定。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"③尼克松一九五八年访问拉丁美洲，拉丁美洲人民用臭鸡蛋、西红柿“迎接”他。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1963\\03\\633q020801.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>洪荒</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>洪荒　插图</FONT>"}]}